
Download the latest SystemRescueCd ISO image from:   http://www.system-rescue-cd.org/Download/


Mount the CD-ROM ISO image


mkdir -p /tmp/cdrom
mount -o loop,exec /media/Dati/OS/Linux/systemrescuecd-x86-5.2.2.iso /tmp/cdrom


cd /tmp/cdrom
bash ./usb_inst.sh

Unmount the ISO image

cd ~
umount /tmp/cdrom
